After the installation is complete, the user can view the functions by clicking on the plug-in. It supports one-click sorting and entering the background. One-click sorting will collect all tab pages and enter the background. At the same time, it also supports right-clicking on the page to add the current page to the in personal space.

安装完成后，用户可以通过点击插件查看到功能，支持一键整理与进入后台，一键整理会收集所有的tab页进入到后台内，同时也支持在页面上右键，从而去将当前页添加到个人的空间内。
